											<td><strong>Bold</strong></td>
											<td>Add two asterisks (**) either side of your text (e.g. **bold**) to put it in bold.</td>
										</tr>
										<tr>
											<td><i>Italic</i></td>
											<td>Put an underscore (_) either side of your text (e.g. _italic_) to put it in italics.</td>
										</tr>
									</tbody>
								</table>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
